From Soup: 154 The atomic parameters used in eqn (13)–(14) to describe the non-bonded interactions of DNA and tether atoms are taken from the AMBER 10 force field. 32 The effects of solvent on electrostatic interactions are treated implicity with the dielectric constant ε assigned a value of 80.
